    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lovers! It honestly breaks my heart a little to post this, but it\u2019s time for my absolute pride and joy to find a new home. I\u2019ve babied this beauty since the day I got it\u2014always garaged, hand-washed every weekend, and driven with nothing but love. The paint still has that incredible showroom shine, and the interior is so clean you\u2019d swear it just rolled off the assembly line. It runs like an absolute dream, smooth as silk and ready for a long weekend cruise. There\u2019s a tiny, barely-there stone chip on the hood if you really go looking for it, but she\u2019s as close to perfect as they come. Come by for a coffee and a look\u2014I promise you won't be disappointed!",
