      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 V8, a masterpiece of atmospheric induction. This unit is mechanically impeccable; the crucial rod bearing service and throttle actuator replacements have been performed preventatively using high-tolerance components. The M-DCT dual-clutch transmission has been recalibrated for crisp, seamless engagement, and the Competition Package (ZCP) suspension geometry remains tight with zero bushing deflection. The paint exhibits deep luster with no evidence of orange peel or panel misalignment, suggesting a life of obsessive climate-controlled storage. With an underskirt as clean as the chassis, this is a turn-key performance machine for the discerning enthusiast who demands zero mechanical compromise.",
